The paper deals with object detection and event recognition using deep convolutional neural networks, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also discusses the integration of different object detection networks, which involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with multimedia analysis (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves the recognition of events from visual data.
